<br>
Yes but the point is, there is no one item that I know of with enough hit points or AC to make a 20% difference in the amount of hp or AC you have.  1 low end haste item makes a 20% difference in the amount of damage you do. <br>
<br>
The reason haste>all IMO is that all other stats grant you incremental improvements... a few hp there, a bit more AC there. In EQ terms, a 20% change in anything is massive.  Haste is the one place you can really get that kind of massive change.<br>
<br>
<br>
Also, all other things being equal, if the mob dies faster you can kill more per hour....  <p><font size="+1">	
