<br>
21% haste item = 21% increase in DAMAGE, NOT a 21% decrease in delay. So a 21% haste item increases damage for every weapon 21%, regardless of dam/delay/ratio<br>
<br>
The delay cap is 9, but it does not apply to haste. It simply means you will not find any weapons with a base delay of under 9.<br>
<br>
