<br>
Haste like I pointed out earlier does not reduce delay. Haste items are listed as percentage increases in damage. Fbss increases all weapons damage by 21%. It does NOT reduce your delay by 21%<br>
<br>
2hs Damage bonus is static and scales up based on the delay of the weapon. The 40+ delay bonus was removed long ago.<br>
1hs damage bonus is static across the board based on level.<br>
